(1974, 1, '2018-12-04 05:34:35', '2018-12-04 05:34:35', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_empty_space height=\"9px\"][media animation=\"none\" link=\"\" image=\"2167\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"About Our Institute\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][vc_column_text]To make the world a better place is what we aim to develop in Arjun students. Our approach therefore is to impart education and create a renewed sense of enlightenment. The magnitude of which is well capable of establishing an individual\'s development to the highest level.\r\n\r\nOur academic excellence is carried forth by our highly trained and qualified teachers who also deeply identify with our vision. The staff members are chosen after a rigorous selection process. As part of our various skill- training programmes, we also impart special training to our teachers on a regular basis to keep them updated about newer trends in the teaching methodology.&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDeveloping the student\'s capabilities from a global perspective by instilling self-confidence in order to be able to contribute to community life, build tolerance &amp;amp; accountability.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Why Choose Us?\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"9px\"][vc_column_text]At Arjun we believe that good learning is majorly dependent upon the quality and competency of the staff members. Hence the institution formulates a deeper understanding of the teacher selection process.A number of guidelines and criteria are carefully put in place to select the best faculty in the teaching industry.Each application from is looked into with great detail and a thorough background check of the candidate is done.The shortlisted candidate is called for a screening interview with our selection panel.The short-listed candidate has to qualify a written aptitude test and demonstrate his teaching skills in order to judge his/her core competencies.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Solution\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"9px\"][vc_column_text][simple-accordian][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Expertise\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"9px\"][media image=\"2372\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Our Institute', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-institute', '', '', '2020-06-30 10:10:11', '2020-06-30 10:10:11', '', 0, 'http://139.59.83.25/~fvowerid/acs/?page_id=1974', 0, 'page', '', 0),
