(2329, 1, '2018-12-22 12:03:47', '2018-12-22 12:03:47', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Arjun convent Higher Secondary School\" font_container=\"tag:h1|font_size:40px|text_align:center\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Admission Policy\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Arjun Convent Higher Secondary School opens admissions every year from class LKG to 8th.A child seeking admission to the school must first get his/her name registered. Registration is no surety for admission. Students are normally registered for admission in the month of April for the next academic session.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Registration\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Registration Forms will be available at our school office. It can be collected from the school on all working days from 8.30 A.M. to 4.30 P.M. Registration is not a guarantee of admission and only includes the child in the process of selection. The School Management reserves the right of Admission and its decision in the matter is final and binding.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Acceptance\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]&nbsp;Acceptance of the admission must be made within 7 days or the offer will stand cancelled. Acceptance of admission also implies acceptance of all school rules &amp; regulations as amended without notice from time to time.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Withdrawal\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Full Fees for the term will be charged if the parents withdraw their child during the course of the academic term or before the term starts. Parents withdrawing the child at the end of a term must inform the school 30 days before the new session starts, otherwise a Penalty Fees would be charged as per school rules and regulations.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Fees Regulation\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]<b>&nbsp;</b>Parents are liable to pay the fees according to the school calendar; if they fail to do so then a Penalty Fee would be charged as per school rules and regulations. If the fee remains unpaid for 2 months from the due date, then the name of the child will be struck out of rolls[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Fees Structure\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]&nbsp;To inquire about the current Fees Structure, kindly contact the school office.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Documents Required At The Time Of Admission\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]\n<ul>\n<li>Passport size photographs of the student</li>\n<li>Photograph of both the parents/guardian.</li>\n<li>Copy of birth certificate issued by the Municipality (duly attested).</li>\n<li>Copy of Child’s Aadhar Card (duly attested).</li>\n<li>Blood Group Report</li>\n<li>Proof of Residence</li>\n<li>Progress Report.</li>\n<li>Transfer Certificate.</li>\n<li>Caste Category Certificate (If belonging to OBC/SC/ST).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Day School', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2303-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-12-22 12:03:47', '2018-12-22 12:03:47', '', 2303, 'http://139.59.83.25/~fvowerid/acs/2018/12/22/2303-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
