ays or the offer will stand cancelled. Acceptance of admission also implies acceptance of all school rules &amp; regulations as amended without notice from time to time.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Withdrawal\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Full Fees for the term will be charged if the parents withdraw their child during the course of the academic term or before the term starts. Parents withdrawing the child at the end of a term must inform the school 30 days before the new session starts, otherwise a Penalty Fees would be charged as per school rules and regulations.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Fees Regulation\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]<b>&nbsp;</b>Parents are liable to pay the fees according to the school calendar; if they fail to do so then a Penalty Fee would be charged as per school rules and regulations. If the fee remains unpaid for 2 months from the due date, then the name of the child will be struck out of rolls[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Fees Structure\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]&nbsp;To inquire about the current Fees Structure, kindly contact the school office.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Documents Required At The Time Of Admission\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Passport size photographs of the student</li>\r\n 	<li>Photograph of both the parents/guardian.</li>\r\n 	<li>Copy of birth certificate issued by the Municipality (duly attested).</li>\r\n 	<li>Copy of Child’s Aadhar Card (duly attested).</li>\r\n 	<li>Blood Group Report</li>\r\n 	<li>Proof of Residence</li>\r\n 	<li>Progress Report.</li>\r\n 	<li>Transfer Certificate.</li>\r\n 	<li>Caste Category Certificate (If belonging to OBC/SC/ST).</li>\r\n 	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Day School', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2303-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-22 11:10:50', '2018-12-22 11:10:50', '', 2303, 'http://139.59.83.25/~fvowerid/acs/2018/12/22/2303-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
