(2341, 1, '2018-12-22 12:06:47', '2018-12-22 12:06:47', '[vc_row][vc_column][block_title title=\"Our Courses\"]\r\n<div class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">With our agenda to provide long term solutions to academic challenges, we envision, drive ahead and endeavour for all students to acquire knowledge and skills to promote sustainable development and future lifestyles.</div>\r\n[/block_title][vc_empty_space][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1544853461922{background-color: #ef801a !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][services_medium style=\"style_3\" icon=\"moon-trophy-star\" icon_color=\"#0c4270\" circle_color=\"#0c4270\" border_color=\"#0c4270\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Life Skills Teaching</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We constantly undertake the part of good teaching practices, ensuring that our teachers are well-equipped in coping with the challenges to explicitly include core content.</span>[/services_medium][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][services_medium style=\"style_3\" icon=\"moon-book\" icon_color=\"#0c4270\" circle_color=\"#0c4270\" border_color=\"#0c4270\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Ensuring Quality Education</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We set sail therefore to further propel the strong foundations of our vision upon which we base our objectives.</span></p>\r\n[/services_medium][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][services_medium style=\"style_3\" icon=\"linecon-icon-study\" icon_color=\"#0c4270\" circle_color=\"#0c4270\" border_color=\"#0c4270\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Teaching Staff</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Our academic excellence is carried forth by our highly trained and qualified teachers who also deeply identify with our vision.</span></p>\r\n[/services_medium][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][services_medium style=\"style_3\" icon=\"steadysets-icon-bars\" icon_color=\"#0c4270\" circle_color=\"#0c4270\" border_color=\"#0c4270\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">The Need For An Inclusive Curriculum</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Education can bring back on track any deviated affair and change the course of the world for the better.</span></p>\r\n[/services_medium][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Courses', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1963-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-22 12:06:47', '2018-12-22 12:06:47', '', 1963, 'http://139.59.83.25/~fvowerid/acs/2018/12/22/1963-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
